  "title": "Technical Support Assistant (Machine/ Equipment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of perform regular checks in inventory software system to ensure inventories are in place</li>\n  <li>responsible in perform regular repairs and maintenance of yard and workshop tools and equipment</li>\n  <li>Maintenance of the tool room through 5S initiatives and good housekeeping practices</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirement</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Nitec in Engineering and relevant</li>\n  <li>Min 1 year of working experience in tooling and vehicle maintenance with experience in inventory system and Microsoft Office suite</li>\n  <li>Class 3 driving license required</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd<br>\nEA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
